    {
      "id": "1924750c-f3ba-8074-a3a1-f1e6f115d945",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors look to explore how different predictors explain differences in final grades and, more specifically, what is the role of the courses internal and external conditions. Results show that behaviour on the LMS explains a small portion of of variance and learner’s internal conditions account for the most part.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1924750c-f3ba-8074-a3a1-f1e6f115d945",
